var notification_timeout = 10000;
var notification_cache = true;
if (!window.console) console = {log: function() {}};

if(typeof String.prototype.trim !== 'function') {
  String.prototype.trim = function() {
    return this.replace(/^\s+|\s+$/g, ''); 
  }
}


/* This function is used to set cookies */
function setCookie(name,value,expires,path,domain,secure) {
  document.cookie = name + "=" + escape (value) +
    ((expires) ? "; expires=" + expires.toGMTString() : "") +
    ((path) ? "; path=" + path : "") +
    ((domain) ? "; domain=" + domain : "") + ((secure) ? "; secure" : "");
}

/* This function is used to get cookies */
function getCookie(name) {
	var prefix = name + "=" ;
	var start = document.cookie.indexOf(prefix); 

	if (start==-1) {
		return null;
	}
	
	var end = document.cookie.indexOf(";", start+prefix.length);
	if (end==-1) {
		end=document.cookie.length;
	}

	var value=document.cookie.substring(start+prefix.length, end) ;
	return unescape(value);
}


function deleteCookie(name,path,domain) {
  if (getCookie(name)) {
    document.cookie = name + "=" +
      ((path) ? "; path=" + path : "") +
      ((domain) ? "; domain=" + domain : "") +
      "; expires=Thu, 01-Jan-70 00:00:01 GMT";
  }
}

var authenticated = 'false';

jQuery(document).ready(function(){
var alreadyCalled = false;

//alert("logged-in:"+authenticated);
//alert("comparison to true, for"+authenticated +", "+ ('true' == authenticated));

if('true' == authenticated){
	//jQuery(".viewnoteTab").mouseout(function(){

//	});

}else{
	//alert("not logged in ");
	jQuery(".notif-cls").on("click",function(){
		//alert('hi');
	  jQuery("#inline_login").hide();
	  //jQuery(".notification .nav-drop").hide();
	  jQuery(".notification").removeClass("notifi");
	});
	updateNonLoggedInUsersTime();
}
function updateNonLoggedInUsersTime(){
	//alert("non_loggedin_time:"+getCookie('non_loggedin_time'));
	var setCookieForTime = getCookie('non_loggedin_time');
	if(null!=setCookieForTime){
		//alert("cookie found to be set to : "+setCookieForTime+" where time since is:"+timeSince(setCookieForTime));
		jQuery("#non_loggedin_time").html(timeSince(setCookieForTime));
	}else{
		var currentTime = new Date().getTime();
		setCookie('non_loggedin_time',currentTime);
	}
}

jQuery(".viewnote").on("click",function(){
	var loggedInClicked = getCookie('loggedin_click');
	if(null!=loggedInClicked){
		jQuery("#notification_count").css("background-color","#075DC1");
	}else{
		if('true' == authenticated){
			setCookie('loggedin_click',1);
			//alert("setting loggedInClicked");
		}
	}
});	

});

</script>

function settextNotification(id){
		if(document.getElementById('txtUseNameNotification').value !=''){
			document.getElementById(id).checked=true;
		}else{
			document.getElementById(id).checked=false;
			document.getElementById('txtUseNameNotification').value='Enter Email id / Login id';
			document.getElementById('txtUseNameNotification').style.color='#999'
		}
	}
function filltxtNotification(id){
		if(document.getElementById('txtUseNameNotification').value=='Enter Email id / Login id')
			document.getElementById('txtUseNameNotification').value=''
		document.getElementById('txtUseNameNotification').style.color='#333'
	}
function validateLoginFormNotification(){
var status = true;
		if(document.getElementById('txtUseNameNotification').value=='Enter Email id / Login id'){
			document.getElementById('txtUseNameNotification').value='';
			status =  false;
		}
		
		if(checkBlankNotification(document.loginFormNotification.j_username,"Login ID")){
			status =  false;
		}
		if(checkBlankNotification(document.loginFormNotification.j_password,"Password")){
			status =  false;
		}
		//update_notification_cookie
		if(status){
			deleteCookie('update_notification_cookie');
		}
		return status;
	}
function checkBlankNotification(field,name){
		if(field.value.trim() == ""){	
			field.value = "";
			field.focus();
			document.getElementById("loginErrNotification").style.display="";
			return true;
		}
		return false;
	}
	
var diff = 1715167381-((new Date().getTime())/1000);


function ellipsize(str, len) {
	if(str.length > len) {
 		return str.substr(0,len) + "...";
	} else {
		return str;
	}
}

function timeSince(previous){

	current =  new Date().getTime()+diff;
	var milleSecondsPerMinute = 60 * 1000;
    var milleSecondsPerHour = milleSecondsPerMinute * 60;
    var milleSecondsPerDay = milleSecondsPerHour * 24;
    var milleSecondsPerMonth = milleSecondsPerDay * 30;
    var milleSecondsPerYear = milleSecondsPerDay * 365;
	
    var elapsed = current - previous;

    if (elapsed < milleSecondsPerMinute) {
         value = Math.round(elapsed/1000) + ' seconds ago';   
    }

    else if (elapsed < milleSecondsPerHour) {
    	value = Math.round(elapsed/milleSecondsPerMinute) + ' minutes ago';   
    }

    else if (elapsed < milleSecondsPerDay ) {
    	value = Math.round(elapsed/milleSecondsPerHour ) + ' hours ago';   
    }

    else if (elapsed < milleSecondsPerMonth) {
    	value =  Math.round(elapsed/milleSecondsPerDay) + ' days ago';   
    }

    else if (elapsed < milleSecondsPerYear) {
    	value = Math.round(elapsed/milleSecondsPerMonth) + ' months ago';   
    }

    else {
    	value = Math.round(elapsed/milleSecondsPerYear ) + ' years ago';   
    }
    //return (value);
    return (value);
}


function updateNotificationComponent(){
 alreadyCalled  =true;	
	var context="";
	if(-1 == window.location.href.indexOf("/candidate/")) {
		  context="/candidate/";
		  //alert("bingo");
	}
	
	
	ajaxController.getLoginId(function(response){
	//alert("updateNotificationComponent,response:"+response)
		if (response != null && response.trim().length > 0) {
			jQuery.ajax({
							cache:notification_cache,
							timeout:notification_timeout,
							url:context+"inbox-notifications.html?from=submit",
							success:function(data){
							var trimLength = 30;
									jQuery("#base_ja").remove();
									jQuery("#base_j").remove();
									jQuery("#base_rv").remove();
									//alert(data);
									var parsedData = JSON.parse(data);
									var theCount = parsedData["count"];
									
									var jaCount = parsedData["jaCount"];
									var jCount = parsedData["jCount"];
									var rvCount = parsedData["rvCount"];
									
									/**
									*UNTILL Resume Contacted is pulled down do the following:
									*/
									//theCount = theCount - jCount;
									/**
									*UNTILL Resume Contacted is pulled down do the following:
									*/
									
									if(theCount >= 0){
										if(theCount >= 0){
											if(theCount <99){
												jQuery("#notification_count").html(theCount);
												setCookie('notification_cookie_count',theCount);
											}else{
												jQuery("#notification_count").html("99+");
												setCookie('notification_cookie_count',"99+");
											}
										}
										
										var isNew = parsedData["new"];
										//alert("new:"+(isNew == true));
										if(isNew == true){
											jQuery("#notification_count").css("background-color","red");
											setCookie('notification_cookie_color','red');
											deleteCookie('loggedin_click');
										}else{
											var loggedInClicked = getCookie('loggedin_click');
											//alert("loggedInClicked:"+loggedInClicked);
											if(null!=loggedInClicked){
												jQuery("#notification_count").css("background-color","#075DC1");
												setCookie('notification_cookie_color','#075DC1');
											}else{
												jQuery("#notification_count").css("background-color","red");
												setCookie('notification_cookie_color','red');
											}
										
										}
									}
									jQuery("#notification_count").show();
									
									/* alert("count:"+parsedData["count"]);							
									alert("jaCount:"+parsedData["jaCount"]);
									alert("jCount:"+parsedData["jCount"]);
									alert("rvCount:"+parsedData["rvCount"]); */
									
									/**
									start-JA
									*/
									if(jaCount){
										if(jaCount <25){
											jQuery("#base .heading span").html("Job alerts ("+jaCount+")");
										}else{
											jQuery("#base .heading span").html("Job alerts (25+)");
										}
										jQuery("#base .heading a#heading-link").attr("href",context+"inbox-home.html?tab=1&from=notification");
									}else{
										jQuery("#base .heading span").html("Job alerts");
										jQuery("#base .heading a#heading-link").attr("href",context+"inbox-home.html?tab=1&from=notification");
									}
									var size =JSON.parse(parsedData["jaData"]).length;
									
									for(var i=0;i<size;i++){
										var id = JSON.parse(parsedData["jaData"])[i].notificationId;
										var subject = JSON.parse(parsedData["jaData"])[i].subject;
										var since = timeSince(JSON.parse(parsedData["jaData"])[i].creationTime);
										jQuery("#base-li-anchor").html(ellipsize(subject,trimLength));
										jQuery("#base-li-anchor").attr("title",subject);
										jQuery("#base-li-anchor").attr("href",context+"inbox-home.html?tab=1&from=notification&showMessage=yes&ObjectId="+id);
										jQuery("#base-li-time").html(since);
										
										var $clonedLI = jQuery("#base-li").clone();
										//$clonedLI.appendTo(".base_li");
										$clonedLI.appendTo("#base-li-data");
										$clonedLI.attr("id","base_ja_"+i);
										$clonedLI.show();
									}
									jQuery("#base").show();
									//alert("DATA:"+$("#base > ul.base_li").html())
									var $cloned = jQuery("#base").clone();
									$cloned.appendTo(".showdiv");
									$cloned.attr("id","base_ja");
									//alert("jaData[0]:"+ (JSON.parse(parsedData["jaData"]).length));
									jQuery("#base > ul span.base_li").html("");
									
									/**
									end-JA
									*/
									
									/**
									start-J
									*/
								   if(jCount){
									 	if(jCount <25){
											jQuery("#base .heading span").html("Mails from recruiters ("+jCount+")");
										}else{
											jQuery("#base .heading span").html("Mails from recruiters (25+)");
										}
										jQuery("#base .heading a#heading-link").attr("href",context+"inbox-home.html?tab=2&from=notification");
									}else{
										jQuery("#base .heading span").html("Mails from recruiters");
										jQuery("#base .heading a#heading-link").attr("href",context+"inbox-home.html?tab=2&from=notification");
									}
									var size =JSON.parse(parsedData["jData"]).length;
									
									for(var i=0;i<size;i++){
										var id = JSON.parse(parsedData["jData"])[i].notificationId;
										var subject = JSON.parse(parsedData["jData"])[i].EmployerName + " contacted you.";
										var since = timeSince(JSON.parse(parsedData["jData"])[i].creationTime);
										jQuery("#base-li-anchor").html(ellipsize(subject,trimLength));
										jQuery("#base-li-anchor").attr("title",subject);
										jQuery("#base-li-anchor").attr("href",context+"inbox-home.html?tab=2&from=notification&showMessage=yes&ObjectId="+id);
										jQuery("#base-li-time").html(since);
										
										var $clonedLI = jQuery("#base-li").clone();
										//$clonedLI.appendTo(".base_li");
										$clonedLI.appendTo("#base-li-data");
										$clonedLI.attr("id","base_j_"+i);
										$clonedLI.show();
									}
									jQuery("#base").show();
									//alert("DATA:"+$("#base > ul.base_li").html())
									var $cloned = jQuery("#base").clone();
									$cloned.appendTo(".showdiv");
									$cloned.attr("id","base_j");
									//alert("jData[0]:"+timeSince(JSON.parse(parsedData["jData"])[0].creationTime));
									jQuery("#base > ul span.base_li").html(""); 
									
									/**
									end-J
									*/
									
									/**
									start-RV
									*/
									if(rvCount > 0){
										if(rvCount <25){
											jQuery("#base .heading span").html("Who's viewed your profile ("+rvCount+")");
										}else{
											jQuery("#base .heading span").html("Who's viewed your profile (25+)");
										}
										jQuery("#base .heading a#heading-link").attr("href",context+"inbox-home.html?tab=5&from=notification");
									}else{
										jQuery("#base .heading span").html("Who's viewed your profile");
										jQuery("#base .heading a#heading-link").attr("href",context+"inbox-home.html?tab=5&from=notification");
									}
									var size =JSON.parse(parsedData["rvData"]).length;
									
									for(var i=0;i<size;i++){
										var id = JSON.parse(parsedData["rvData"])[i].notificationId;
										var subject = JSON.parse(parsedData["rvData"])[i].subject;
										var employerName = JSON.parse(parsedData["rvData"])[i].EmployerName + " viewed your resume.";
										var since = timeSince(JSON.parse(parsedData["rvData"])[i].creationTime);
										if(null!=employerName && employerName.length > 0){
											jQuery("#base-li-anchor").html(ellipsize(employerName,trimLength));
											jQuery("#base-li-anchor").attr("title",employerName);
										}else{
											jQuery("#base-li-anchor").html("Resume Viewed");
										}
										jQuery("#base-li-anchor").attr("href",context+"inbox-home.html?tab=5&from=notification&showMessage=yes&ObjectId="+id);
										jQuery("#base-li-time").html(since);
										
										var $clonedLI = jQuery("#base-li").clone();
										//$clonedLI.appendTo(".base_li");
										$clonedLI.appendTo("#base-li-data");
										$clonedLI.attr("id","base_rv_"+i);
										$clonedLI.show();
									}
									jQuery("#base").show();
									//alert("DATA:"+$("#base > ul.base_li").html())
									var $cloned = jQuery("#base").clone();
									$cloned.appendTo(".showdiv");
									$cloned.attr("id","base_rv");
									//alert("rvData[0]:"+timeSince(JSON.parse(parsedData["rvData"])[0].employerName));
									jQuery("#base > ul span.base_li").html("");
									/**
									end-RV
									*/
									
									jQuery("#base").hide();
									jQuery("li#base-li").hide();
								},
							complete:function(){
								console.log("complete... inbox-notifications");
								jQuery("#inline_login").hide();
   								jQuery("#non_loggedin").hide();
   								alreadyCalled  = false;
							},
							error: function(x, t, m) {
								console.log("Error message"+m);
								 var randomnumber=Math.floor(Math.random()*100000001);
								 var nlpurl='https://alerts.timesjobs.com/naf/nlpTracking.html?captchaType='+context+"inbox-notifications.html?from=submit"+'&op=respTracking#'+randomnumber;
								 ping(nlpurl);
						        jQuery("#error").show();
							}
						});
			
		}else{
					jQuery("#base_ja").remove();
					jQuery("#base_j").remove();
					jQuery("#base_rv").remove();
					if(0 == race){
						jQuery("#non_loggedin").show();
					}
					
					
					var hideCountCookie = getCookie('hide_nologgedin_count');
					if(null != hideCountCookie){
						/*This is commented because for non logged in user default count 1 is being hidden.*/
						//jQuery("#notification_count").hide();
					}else{
						jQuery("#notification_count").css("background-color","red");
						jQuery("#notification_count").show();
					}
					alreadyCalled  = false;				
		}
	});
}

var updateNotificationCookie = getCookie('update_notification_cookie');
//alert("updateNotificationCookie: "+updateNotificationCookie);
if(null == updateNotificationCookie || updateNotificationCookie==''){
	updateNotificationComponentWithIECheck();
	setCookie('update_notification_cookie',1);
	//alert("cookie set");
	scheduleNotificationCookieToDie();
}else{
	if('true' == authenticated){
		//alert("updating from cookie!!!");
		var notificationCookieCount = getCookie('notification_cookie_count');
		if(null==notificationCookieCount){
			updateNotificationComponent();
		}
		updateNotificationFromCookie();
	}else{
		//alert("not updating from cookie!!!");
		updateNotificationComponentWithIECheck();
	}
}

function scheduleNotificationCookieToDie(){
	setTimeout(function() {
	      deleteCookie('update_notification_cookie');
	      deleteCookie('notification_cookie_count');
	      deleteCookie('notification_cookie_color');
	},5*60*1000);
}

function updateNotificationFromCookie(){
console.log("cookie set for updateNotificationCookie, not making server call.");
		var notificationCookieCount = getCookie('notification_cookie_count');
		//alert("not setting cookie"+updateNotificationCookie);
		if(null!=notificationCookieCount){
			jQuery("#notification_count").html(""+notificationCookieCount);
		}else{
			jQuery("#notification_count").html("1");
		}
		var notificationCookieColor = getCookie('notification_cookie_color');
		//alert("cookie color"+notificationCookieColor);
		if(null!=notificationCookieCount){
			jQuery("#notification_count").css("background-color",notificationCookieColor);
		}else{
			jQuery("#notification_count").css("background-color","red");
		}
		jQuery("#notification_count").show();
}

function updateNotificationComponentWithIECheck(){
<!--[if gte IE 9]> 
		updateNotificationComponent();
	<!--<![endif]-->
	<!--[if lt IE 9]> 
   		jQuery(document).ready(function() {
			updateNotificationComponent();
		});
	<!--<![endif]-->
}

<script type="text/javascript"> 

$(document).ready(function(){
		
		jQuery("#txtKeywords").blur(function() {
			let txtKeywordsValue__ = 'Enter Skills, Designation, etc';
			let txtKeywords__ = $('#txtKeywords').val();
			if(txtKeywordsValue__ === txtKeywords__){
				return ;
			}
			let searchTextText__ = $('#searchTextText').val();
			let searchTextSrc__ = $('#searchTextSrc').val();
			
			console.log(' .......... txtKeywords__ : '+txtKeywords__);
			console.log(' .......... searchTextText__ : '+searchTextText__);
			
			
			// if skill box is not empty
			if(txtKeywords__ != undefined && txtKeywords__.trim() != ''){
				// if autosuggest-skill is empty and skill-box is not empty, is free-text
				if(searchTextText__ === undefined || searchTextText__.trim() === ''){
					$('#searchTextSrc').val('ft');
					//console.log(' ......... set ft 1')
				// if skill-box is not empty and autosuggest-skill is not empty and skill-box and autosuggest-skill don't match	
				}else if(searchTextText__ != undefined && searchTextText__.trim() != '' && searchTextText__ != txtKeywords__){
					$('#searchTextSrc').val('ft');
					//console.log(' ......... set ft 2')
				}
			} 
		
			
			
		});
	});


  var ssCounterSFB=0;
	function openSecondSuggestionSFB(theSelectedSuggestionText){
		if(ssCounterSFB < 5){
			ajaxController.getSuggestedSkillList(theSelectedSuggestionText,"","SKILL",8,true,cb_openSecondSuggestionSFB);
		}else{
			console.log("CAND-131 Not showing 2nd suggestion.");
		}
	}

	function cb_openSecondSuggestionSFB(result){
		//alert("cb_openSecondSuggestion:"+result);
		var splitData = (""+result).split(",");
		var li_data = "";
		var dataLength = splitData.length;
	    var text = jQuery("#txtKeywords").val();
	    text =text.toLowerCase();
	    if(dataLength >1){
			for(i=0;i<dataLength;i++){
	            if(text.indexOf(splitData[i].toLowerCase()) < 0){
	                var hyperlink =  "javascript:secondSelectionClickedSFB('"+encodeURI(splitData[i])+"');";
					li_data+="<li><a href="+hyperlink+">"+splitData[i]+"</a></li>";
				}
			}
			jQuery("#autoSuggestList2ndKeywordsListSFB ul").html(li_data);
			jQuery("#autoSuggestList2ndKeywordsListSFB").slideDown(300);
			//ssCounterSFB = ssCounterSFB  + 1;
		}		
	}

	function secondSelectionClickedSFB(that){
		//alert("that:"+that);
		_gaq.push(['_trackEvent','Click2Ad','tj_skillsuggestion']);
		jQuery("#autoSuggestList2ndKeywordsListSFB").hide();
		var text = jQuery("#txtKeywords").val();
		var text2 = text.toLowerCase() + ",";
		var that2 = that.toLowerCase();
		var res = text2.split(",");
		var exists = false;
		for(i in res){
			if(null!=res[i] && res[i].length > 0 && res[i]+"".trim() === that2){
				exists = true;
				break;
			} 
		}
		//var index = text2.search(new RegExp(that2, "i"));
		//console.log("exists:"+exists);
		if(!exists){
		
			that1_ = that.trim().split(' ');
			if(that1_.length > 1){
				that1_ = '"'+that+'"';
			}else{
				that1_ = that;
			}
			
			try{
				var s_ = $('#searchTextText').val();
				$('#searchTextText').val(s_ + ","+ that1_.trim());
				s_ = '';
			}catch(ex){
				console.log(ex)
			}
			
			
		
			jQuery("#txtKeywords").val(text +","+ that1_);
			jQuery("#txtKeywords").focus();
			that1_ ='';
		}
		openSecondSuggestionSFB(that);
	}
jQuery(document).ready(function(){
	jQuery('#quickSearchBean input[type="text"]').DefaultInputValue();
})

function BasicResFileUpload(){
		//alert('uploaded re loaded');
		new AjaxUpload('resumeFile_basic', {
			action:'/candidate/servlet/FileUploadServlet',
			//responseType: 'json',
			responseType: 'true',
			name: 'resumeFile_basic',
			onSubmit : function() {
				//alert('11');
				document.getElementById("uploadResume_basic").style.display="none";
				document.getElementById("uploadingResume_basic").style.display="block";
			},
			onComplete : function(file,response){
				var displayFilename=file;
				if(file.length >18){
					displayFilename=file.substring(0,18)+"..";
				}
				response = response.replace(/'/g , '"');
				var jsonObj = jQuery.parseJSON(response);
				jsonObj["filename"] = displayFilename;
				ajaxController.setSessionAttribute('tjindexResumeUploadMsg', jsonObj["MESSAGE"]);
				response = JSON.stringify(jsonObj);
				ajaxController.setSessionAttribute('tjindexResumeUpload', response);
				//window.open('/candidate/register.html', '_blank');
				window.location ='/candidate/register.html';
			}	
		});	
	}
	BasicResFileUpload();
  </script>

	    fc_CSS.setAttribute('rel', 'stylesheet');
	    var fc_isSecured = (window.location && window.location.protocol == 'https:');
	    var fc_lang = document.getElementsByTagName('html')[0].getAttribute('lang');
	    var fc_rtlLanguages = ['ar', 'he'];
	    var fc_rtlSuffix = (fc_rtlLanguages.indexOf(fc_lang) >= 0) ? '-rtl' : '';
	    fc_CSS.setAttribute('type', 'text/css');
	    fc_CSS.setAttribute('href', ((fc_isSecured) ? 'https://d36mpcpuzc4ztk.cloudfront.net' : 'http://assets1.chat.freshdesk.com') + '/css/visitor' + fc_rtlSuffix + '.css');
	    document.getElementsByTagName('head')[0].appendChild(fc_CSS);
	    var fc_JS = document.createElement('script');
	    fc_JS.type = 'text/javascript';
	    fc_JS.defer = true;
	    fc_JS.src = ((fc_isSecured) ? 'https://d36mpcpuzc4ztk.cloudfront.net' : 'http://assets.chat.freshdesk.com') + '/js/visitor.js';

<script type="text/javascript">
  $(document).ready(function(){
    $('.collapsible').collapsible();
	//var bodyHeight = $("body").height()-1000;
	 // alert(bodyHeight);
//	$('.inside-lhs').pushpin({
//      top: 326,
//      bottom: bodyHeight,
//      offset: 20
//    });
  });
  
  
  
  $(document).ready(function(){
	  $('.view-more').on('click', function () {
          var targetDivId = $(this).data('target');
          $('#' + targetDivId).show();
          console.log('called');
      });
	  
	  $('.close-modal').on('click', function () {
	        $(this).closest('.search-pop-filter').hide();
	  });
  });
	  $(document).ready(function () {
	      $('#filterCompanyInput').on('input', function () {
	        var searchTerm = $(this).val().toLowerCase();
	        filterList('filterCompanyInput',searchTerm);
	      });
	      $('#filterFunAreaInput').on('input', function () {
	        var searchTerm = $(this).val().toLowerCase();
	        filterList('filterFunAreaInput',searchTerm);
	      });
	      $('#filterIndustryInput').on('input', function () {
	        var searchTerm = $(this).val().toLowerCase();
	        filterList('filterIndustryInput',searchTerm);
	      });
	      $('#filterSalaryInput').on('input', function () {
	        var searchTerm = $(this).val().toLowerCase();
	        filterList('filterSalaryInput',searchTerm);
	      });
	      $('#filterSpecializationInput').on('input', function () {
	        var searchTerm = $(this).val().toLowerCase();
	        filterList('filterSpecializationInput',searchTerm);
	      });

	      function filterList(id,searchTerm) {
	        $('#'+id+'-searchList label').each(function () {
	          var listItemText = $(this).text().toLowerCase();
	          if (listItemText.includes(searchTerm)) {
	            $(this).show();
	          } else {
	            $(this).hide();
	          }
	        });
	      }
	    });
	    var compNamesToSearch = new Map();
	    var compNamesToAdd = "";
	    var compNamesToRemove = "";
	    var urlToSearch = "";
	    function addCompNames(id,url,compName){
	    	urlToSearch = url;
	    	if($('#'+id).prop("checked") == true){
	    		compNamesToSearch.set(compName,true); // addition of company name search
	    	}else{
	    		compNamesToSearch.set(compName,false); // removal of company from search
	    	}
	    	console.log(' urlToSearch : '+urlToSearch+", compNamesToSearch : "+JSON.stringify(compNamesToSearch));
	    }
	    var jobFunNamesToSearch = new Map();
	    var jobFunCodes = new Map();
	    var jobFunNamesToAdd = "";
	    var jobFunNamesToRemove = "";
	    function addJobFunNames(id,url,jobFunName,code){
	    	urlToSearch = url;
	    	jobFunCodes.set(jobFunName,code)
	    	if($('#'+id).prop("checked") == true){
	    		jobFunNamesToSearch.set(jobFunName,true); // addition of jobFun name search
	    	}else{
	    		jobFunNamesToSearch.set(jobFunName,false); // removal of jobFun from search
	    	}
	    	console.log(' urlToSearch : '+urlToSearch+", jobFunNamesToSearch : "+JSON.stringify(jobFunNamesToSearch));
	    }
	    var industryCodeToSearch = new Map();
	    var industryToAdd = "";
	    var industryToRemove = "";
	    function addIndustryNames(id,url,code){
	    	urlToSearch = url;
	    	if($('#'+id).prop("checked") == true){
	    		industryCodeToSearch.set(code,true); // addition of industry code search
	    	}else{
	    		industryCodeToSearch.set(code,false); // removal of industry code from search
	    	}
	    	console.log(' urlToSearch : '+urlToSearch+", industryCodeToSearch : "+JSON.stringify(industryCodeToSearch));
	    }
	    var salaryToSearch = new Map();
	    var salaryToAdd = "";
	    var salaryToRemove = "";
	    function addSalary(id,url,lowSal,highSal){
	    	urlToSearch = url;
	    	if($('#'+id).prop("checked") == true){
	    		salaryToSearch.set(lowSal+"-"+highSal,true); // addition of salary code search
	    	}else{
	    		salaryToSearch.set(lowSal+"-"+highSal,false); // removal of salary code from search
	    	}
	    	console.log(' urlToSearch : '+urlToSearch+", salaryToSearch : "+JSON.stringify(salaryToSearch));
	    }
	    var specializationUrl = "";
	    function addSpecialization(url){
	    	specializationUrl = url;
	    }
	    function getSRPResultByDwr2(filterFor){
	    	if(filterFor=='COMPANY'){
	    		compNamesToAdd = '';
	    		compNamesToRemove = '';
		    	if(compNamesToSearch.size>0){
		    		for (const [key, value] of compNamesToSearch.entries()) {
					  console.log(key, value);
					  if(value==true){
					  	if(compNamesToAdd.trim().length == 0){
					  		compNamesToAdd = key;
					  	}else{
					  		compNamesToAdd = compNamesToAdd +','+key;
					  	}
					  }
					  if(value==false){
					  	if(compNamesToRemove.trim().length == 0){
					  		compNamesToRemove = key;
					  	}else{
					  		compNamesToRemove = compNamesToRemove +','+key;
					  	}
					  }
					}
					console.log(' compNamesToAdd ',compNamesToAdd)
					console.log(' compNamesToRemove ',compNamesToRemove)
					urlToSearch = urlToSearch + '&'
					if(compNamesToAdd.trim().length>1){
						urlToSearch = urlToSearch + 'clusterName=CLUSTER_COMP&undokey=compCluster&compCluster='+compNamesToAdd+'&'
					}
					if(compNamesToRemove.trim().length>1){
						urlToSearch = urlToSearch + 'undo=compCluster&undoValue='+compNamesToRemove+'&'
					}
		    	}
	    	}else if(filterFor=='JOBFUN'){
	    		var jobFunCodes_ = '';
	    		jobFunNamesToAdd = '';
	    		jobFunNamesToRemove = '';
		    	if(jobFunNamesToSearch.size>0){
		    		for (const [key, value] of jobFunNamesToSearch.entries()) {
					  console.log(key, value);
					  if(value==true){
					  	if(jobFunNamesToAdd.trim().length == 0){
					  		jobFunNamesToAdd = key;
					  	}else{
					  		jobFunNamesToAdd = jobFunNamesToAdd +','+key;
					  	}
					  	if(jobFunCodes_.trim().length == 0){
					  		jobFunCodes_ = jobFunCodes.get(key);
					  	}else{
							jobFunCodes_ = jobFunCodes_ + ',' + jobFunCodes.get(key);					  	
					  	}
					  }
					  if(value==false){
					  	if(jobFunNamesToRemove.trim().length == 0){
					  		jobFunNamesToRemove = key;
					  	}else{
					  		jobFunNamesToRemove = jobFunNamesToRemove +','+key;
					  	}
					  }
					}
					
					console.log(' jobFunNamesToAdd ',jobFunNamesToAdd)
					console.log(' jobFunNamesToRemove ',jobFunNamesToRemove)
					urlToSearch = urlToSearch + '&'
					if(jobFunNamesToAdd.trim().length>1){
						urlToSearch = urlToSearch + 'clusterName=CLUSTER_FA&undokey=cboPresFuncArea&cboPresFuncArea='+jobFunCodes_+'&'
					}
					if(jobFunNamesToRemove.trim().length>1){
						urlToSearch = urlToSearch + 'undo=cboPresFuncArea'+'&'
					}
		    	}
	    	}else if(filterFor=='INDUSTRY'){
	    		industryToAdd = "";
	    		industryToRemove = "";
		    	if(industryCodeToSearch.size>0){
		    		for (const [key, value] of industryCodeToSearch.entries()) {
					  console.log(key, value);
					  if(value==true){
					  	if(industryToAdd.trim().length == 0){
					  		industryToAdd = key;
					  	}else{
					  		industryToAdd = industryToAdd +','+key;
					  	}
					  }
					  if(value==false){
					  	if(industryToRemove.trim().length == 0){
					  		industryToRemove = key;
					  	}else{
					  		industryToRemove = industryToRemove +','+key;
					  	}
					  }
					}
					
					console.log(' industryToAdd ',industryToAdd)
					console.log(' industryToRemove ',industryToRemove)
					urlToSearch = urlToSearch + '&'
					if(industryToAdd.trim().length>1){
						urlToSearch = urlToSearch + 'clusterName=CLUSTER_IND&undokey=cboIndustry&cboIndustry='+industryToAdd+'&'
					}
					if(industryToRemove.trim().length>1){
						urlToSearch = urlToSearch + 'undo=cboIndustry'+'&'
					}
		    	}
	    	}
	    	else if(filterFor=='SALARY'){
	    		salaryToAdd = "";
	    		salaryToRemove = "";
		    	if(salaryToSearch.size>0){
		    		for (const [key, value] of salaryToSearch.entries()) {
					  console.log(key, value);
					  if(value==true){
					  	if(salaryToAdd.trim().length == 0){
					  		salaryToAdd = key;
					  	}else{
					  		salaryToAdd = salaryToAdd +','+key;
					  	}
					  }
					  if(value==false){
					  	if(salaryToRemove.trim().length == 0){
					  		salaryToRemove = key;
					  	}else{
					  		salaryToRemove = salaryToRemove +','+key;
					  	}
					  }
					}
					
					console.log(' salaryToAdd ',salaryToAdd)
					console.log(' salaryToRemove ',salaryToRemove)
					urlToSearch = urlToSearch + '&'
					if(salaryToAdd.trim().length>1){
						const salaries = salaryToAdd.split(',');
						let ls = '';
						let hs = '';
						for(const sal of salaries){
							let lhs = sal.split('-');
							if(ls.trim().length == 0){
								ls = lhs[0];
							}else{
								ls = ls +','+ lhs[0]; 
							}
							if(hs.trim().length == 0){
								hs = lhs[1];
							}else{
								hs = hs +','+ lhs[1]; 
							}
						}
						urlToSearch = removeParamFromURI(urlToSearch, 'clusterName');
						urlToSearch = removeParamFromURI(urlToSearch, 'undokey');
						urlToSearch = removeParamFromURI(urlToSearch, 'txtHighSalary');
						urlToSearch = removeParamFromURI(urlToSearch, 'txtLowSalary');
						urlToSearch = urlToSearch + 'clusterName=CLUSTER_CTC&undokey=txtLowSalary&txtHighSalary='+hs+'&txtLowSalary='+ls+'&'
					}
					if(salaryToRemove.trim().length>1){
						urlToSearch = urlToSearch + 'undo=txtLowSalary&txtHighSalary='+hs+'&'
					}
		    	}
	    	}
	    	else if(filterFor=='SPECIALIZATION'){
	    		urlToSearch = specializationUrl;
	    	}
	    	
	    	console.log(' urlToSearch : '+urlToSearch);
	    	getSRPResultByDwr(urlToSearch)
	    }
	    function removeParamFromURI(uri,paramName){
	    	let startIndex = uri.indexOf(paramName);
	    	let endIndex = uri.indexOf('&', startIndex) - startIndex+1;
	    	let str = uri.substr(startIndex, endIndex);
	    	console.log(str, startIndex, endIndex)
	    	console.log(' url before ', uri);
	    	uri = uri.replace(str, '')
	    	console.log(' url after ', uri);
	    	return uri;
	    }
</script>

  </div>

                    <input id="ctc2_7" type="radio" name="ctcMap" onclick="addSalary('ctc2_7','/job-search.html?clusterName=CLUSTER_CTC&refineBy=dateWise&from=undo&luceneResultSize=25&postWeek=60&searchType=Home_Search&cboPresFuncArea=35&undokey=txtLowSalary&txtLowSalary=5000000&txtHighSalary=10000000&gadLink=50+ lacs','5000000','10000000');trackAjaxSRPresult('/job-search.html?clusterName=CLUSTER_CTC&refineBy=dateWise&from=undo&luceneResultSize=25&postWeek=60&searchType=Home_Search&cboPresFuncArea=35&undokey=txtLowSalary&txtLowSalary=5000000&txtHighSalary=10000000&gadLink=50+ lacs','50+ lacs');">

<li id="tabremote">

    <div class="cluster-scroll ">

<script type="text/javascript">
  $(document).ready(function(){
    $('.collapsible').collapsible();
	//var bodyHeight = $("body").height()-1000;
	 // alert(bodyHeight);
//	$('.inside-lhs').pushpin({
//      top: 326,
//      bottom: bodyHeight,
//      offset: 20
//    });
  });
  
  
  
  $(document).ready(function(){
	  $('.view-more').on('click', function () {
          var targetDivId = $(this).data('target');
          $('#' + targetDivId).show();
          console.log('called');
      });
	  
	  $('.close-modal').on('click', function () {
	        $(this).closest('.search-pop-filter').hide();
	  });
  });
	  $(document).ready(function () {
	      $('#filterCompanyInput').on('input', function () {
	        var searchTerm = $(this).val().toLowerCase();
	        filterList('filterCompanyInput',searchTerm);
	      });
	      $('#filterFunAreaInput').on('input', function () {
	        var searchTerm = $(this).val().toLowerCase();
	        filterList('filterFunAreaInput',searchTerm);
	      });
	      $('#filterIndustryInput').on('input', function () {
	        var searchTerm = $(this).val().toLowerCase();
	        filterList('filterIndustryInput',searchTerm);
	      });
	      $('#filterSalaryInput').on('input', function () {
	        var searchTerm = $(this).val().toLowerCase();
	        filterList('filterSalaryInput',searchTerm);
	      });
	      $('#filterSpecializationInput').on('input', function () {
	        var searchTerm = $(this).val().toLowerCase();
	        filterList('filterSpecializationInput',searchTerm);
	      });

	      function filterList(id,searchTerm) {
	        $('#'+id+'-searchList label').each(function () {
	          var listItemText = $(this).text().toLowerCase();
	          if (listItemText.includes(searchTerm)) {
	            $(this).show();
	          } else {
	            $(this).hide();
	          }
	        });
	      }
	    });
	    var compNamesToSearch = new Map();
	    var compNamesToAdd = "";
	    var compNamesToRemove = "";
	    var urlToSearch = "";
	    function addCompNames(id,url,compName){
	    	urlToSearch = url;
	    	if($('#'+id).prop("checked") == true){
	    		compNamesToSearch.set(compName,true); // addition of company name search
	    	}else{
	    		compNamesToSearch.set(compName,false); // removal of company from search
	    	}
	    	console.log(' urlToSearch : '+urlToSearch+", compNamesToSearch : "+JSON.stringify(compNamesToSearch));
	    }
	    var jobFunNamesToSearch = new Map();
	    var jobFunCodes = new Map();
	    var jobFunNamesToAdd = "";
	    var jobFunNamesToRemove = "";
	    function addJobFunNames(id,url,jobFunName,code){
	    	urlToSearch = url;
	    	jobFunCodes.set(jobFunName,code)
	    	if($('#'+id).prop("checked") == true){
	    		jobFunNamesToSearch.set(jobFunName,true); // addition of jobFun name search
	    	}else{
	    		jobFunNamesToSearch.set(jobFunName,false); // removal of jobFun from search
	    	}
	    	console.log(' urlToSearch : '+urlToSearch+", jobFunNamesToSearch : "+JSON.stringify(jobFunNamesToSearch));
	    }
	    var industryCodeToSearch = new Map();
	    var industryToAdd = "";
	    var industryToRemove = "";
	    function addIndustryNames(id,url,code){
	    	urlToSearch = url;
	    	if($('#'+id).prop("checked") == true){
	    		industryCodeToSearch.set(code,true); // addition of industry code search
	    	}else{
	    		industryCodeToSearch.set(code,false); // removal of industry code from search
	    	}
	    	console.log(' urlToSearch : '+urlToSearch+", industryCodeToSearch : "+JSON.stringify(industryCodeToSearch));
	    }
	    var salaryToSearch = new Map();
	    var salaryToAdd = "";
	    var salaryToRemove = "";
	    function addSalary(id,url,lowSal,highSal){
	    	urlToSearch = url;
	    	if($('#'+id).prop("checked") == true){
	    		salaryToSearch.set(lowSal+"-"+highSal,true); // addition of salary code search
	    	}else{
	    		salaryToSearch.set(lowSal+"-"+highSal,false); // removal of salary code from search
	    	}
	    	console.log(' urlToSearch : '+urlToSearch+", salaryToSearch : "+JSON.stringify(salaryToSearch));
	    }
	    var specializationUrl = "";
	    function addSpecialization(url){
	    	specializationUrl = url;
	    }
	    function getSRPResultByDwr2(filterFor){
	    	if(filterFor=='COMPANY'){
	    		compNamesToAdd = '';
	    		compNamesToRemove = '';
		    	if(compNamesToSearch.size>0){
		    		for (const [key, value] of compNamesToSearch.entries()) {
					  console.log(key, value);
					  if(value==true){
					  	if(compNamesToAdd.trim().length == 0){
					  		compNamesToAdd = key;
					  	}else{
					  		compNamesToAdd = compNamesToAdd +','+key;
					  	}
					  }
					  if(value==false){
					  	if(compNamesToRemove.trim().length == 0){
					  		compNamesToRemove = key;
					  	}else{
					  		compNamesToRemove = compNamesToRemove +','+key;
					  	}
					  }
					}
					console.log(' compNamesToAdd ',compNamesToAdd)
					console.log(' compNamesToRemove ',compNamesToRemove)
					urlToSearch = urlToSearch + '&'
					if(compNamesToAdd.trim().length>1){
						urlToSearch = urlToSearch + 'clusterName=CLUSTER_COMP&undokey=compCluster&compCluster='+compNamesToAdd+'&'
					}
					if(compNamesToRemove.trim().length>1){
						urlToSearch = urlToSearch + 'undo=compCluster&undoValue='+compNamesToRemove+'&'
					}
		    	}
	    	}else if(filterFor=='JOBFUN'){
	    		var jobFunCodes_ = '';
	    		jobFunNamesToAdd = '';
	    		jobFunNamesToRemove = '';
		    	if(jobFunNamesToSearch.size>0){
		    		for (const [key, value] of jobFunNamesToSearch.entries()) {
					  console.log(key, value);
					  if(value==true){
					  	if(jobFunNamesToAdd.trim().length == 0){
					  		jobFunNamesToAdd = key;
					  	}else{
					  		jobFunNamesToAdd = jobFunNamesToAdd +','+key;
					  	}
					  	if(jobFunCodes_.trim().length == 0){
					  		jobFunCodes_ = jobFunCodes.get(key);
					  	}else{
							jobFunCodes_ = jobFunCodes_ + ',' + jobFunCodes.get(key);					  	
					  	}
					  }
					  if(value==false){
					  	if(jobFunNamesToRemove.trim().length == 0){
					  		jobFunNamesToRemove = key;
					  	}else{
					  		jobFunNamesToRemove = jobFunNamesToRemove +','+key;
					  	}
					  }
					}
					
					console.log(' jobFunNamesToAdd ',jobFunNamesToAdd)
					console.log(' jobFunNamesToRemove ',jobFunNamesToRemove)
					urlToSearch = urlToSearch + '&'
					if(jobFunNamesToAdd.trim().length>1){
						urlToSearch = urlToSearch + 'clusterName=CLUSTER_FA&undokey=cboPresFuncArea&cboPresFuncArea='+jobFunCodes_+'&'
					}
					if(jobFunNamesToRemove.trim().length>1){
						urlToSearch = urlToSearch + 'undo=cboPresFuncArea'+'&'
					}
		    	}
	    	}else if(filterFor=='INDUSTRY'){
	    		industryToAdd = "";
	    		industryToRemove = "";
		    	if(industryCodeToSearch.size>0){
		    		for (const [key, value] of industryCodeToSearch.entries()) {
					  console.log(key, value);
					  if(value==true){
					  	if(industryToAdd.trim().length == 0){
					  		industryToAdd = key;
					  	}else{
					  		industryToAdd = industryToAdd +','+key;
					  	}
					  }
					  if(value==false){
					  	if(industryToRemove.trim().length == 0){
					  		industryToRemove = key;
					  	}else{
					  		industryToRemove = industryToRemove +','+key;
					  	}
					  }
					}
					
					console.log(' industryToAdd ',industryToAdd)
					console.log(' industryToRemove ',industryToRemove)
					urlToSearch = urlToSearch + '&'
					if(industryToAdd.trim().length>1){
						urlToSearch = urlToSearch + 'clusterName=CLUSTER_IND&undokey=cboIndustry&cboIndustry='+industryToAdd+'&'
					}
					if(industryToRemove.trim().length>1){
						urlToSearch = urlToSearch + 'undo=cboIndustry'+'&'
					}
		    	}
	    	}
	    	else if(filterFor=='SALARY'){
	    		salaryToAdd = "";
	    		salaryToRemove = "";
		    	if(salaryToSearch.size>0){
		    		for (const [key, value] of salaryToSearch.entries()) {
					  console.log(key, value);
					  if(value==true){
					  	if(salaryToAdd.trim().length == 0){
					  		salaryToAdd = key;
					  	}else{
					  		salaryToAdd = salaryToAdd +','+key;
					  	}
					  }
					  if(value==false){
					  	if(salaryToRemove.trim().length == 0){
					  		salaryToRemove = key;
					  	}else{
					  		salaryToRemove = salaryToRemove +','+key;
					  	}
					  }
					}
					
					console.log(' salaryToAdd ',salaryToAdd)
					console.log(' salaryToRemove ',salaryToRemove)
					urlToSearch = urlToSearch + '&'
					if(salaryToAdd.trim().length>1){
						const salaries = salaryToAdd.split(',');
						let ls = '';
						let hs = '';
						for(const sal of salaries){
							let lhs = sal.split('-');
							if(ls.trim().length == 0){
								ls = lhs[0];
							}else{
								ls = ls +','+ lhs[0]; 
							}
							if(hs.trim().length == 0){
								hs = lhs[1];
							}else{
								hs = hs +','+ lhs[1]; 
							}
						}
						urlToSearch = removeParamFromURI(urlToSearch, 'clusterName');
						urlToSearch = removeParamFromURI(urlToSearch, 'undokey');
						urlToSearch = removeParamFromURI(urlToSearch, 'txtHighSalary');
						urlToSearch = removeParamFromURI(urlToSearch, 'txtLowSalary');
						urlToSearch = urlToSearch + 'clusterName=CLUSTER_CTC&undokey=txtLowSalary&txtHighSalary='+hs+'&txtLowSalary='+ls+'&'
					}
					if(salaryToRemove.trim().length>1){
						urlToSearch = urlToSearch + 'undo=txtLowSalary&txtHighSalary='+hs+'&'
					}
		    	}
	    	}
	    	else if(filterFor=='SPECIALIZATION'){
	    		urlToSearch = specializationUrl;
	    	}
	    	
	    	console.log(' urlToSearch : '+urlToSearch);
	    	getSRPResultByDwr(urlToSearch)
	    }
	    function removeParamFromURI(uri,paramName){
	    	let startIndex = uri.indexOf(paramName);
	    	let endIndex = uri.indexOf('&', startIndex) - startIndex+1;
	    	let str = uri.substr(startIndex, endIndex);
	    	console.log(str, startIndex, endIndex)
	    	console.log(' url before ', uri);
	    	uri = uri.replace(str, '')
	    	console.log(' url after ', uri);
	    	return uri;
	    }
</script>
 
  </div>

	var dataImageLoader="<img src='https://static.timesjobs.com/images_cand/tj_images/personlisation/loader.gif' alt='Loading' class='data-loading'>";
	jQuery(document).ready(function() {
				/**********For changing counts on search pannel Top**************/
				var searchNameType='';
				console.info("searchNameType=="+searchNameType);
				var resultCounts = jQuery("#onlyJobsResulCounts").html();
				console.info("resultCounts=="+resultCounts);
				if(searchNameType!='expiry'){
					jQuery("#totolResultCountsId").html(resultCounts);
					jQuery("#totolResultCountsClosingId").html(resultCounts);
					jQuery("#totolResultCountsId").show();
					jQuery("#jobCountTextId").show();
					jQuery("#srCountDisplayId").removeClass('active');
					jQuery("#totolResultCountsIdLink").hide();
					jQuery("#displayExpiryJobCount").removeClass('deactive');
					jQuery("#refine-opt-search-datewise").show();
				}else{					
					jQuery("#totolResultCountsClosingId").html(resultCounts);
					jQuery("#totolResultCountsId").hide();
					jQuery("#jobCountTextId").hide();
					jQuery("#totolResultCountsIdLink").show();
					jQuery("#srCountDisplayId").addClass('active');
					jQuery("#displayExpiryJobCount").addClass('deactive');
					jQuery("#refine-opt-search-datewise").hide();
					
				}
				if(''== false || '' =='false'){
					var expiryJobCount=jQuery("#onlyExpiredJobsResulCount").html();
					jQuery("#expiryJobCount").html(expiryJobCount);
					if(chkNull(expiryJobCount) && expiryJobCount >0){
						jQuery("#displayExpiryJobCount").show();
					}else{
						jQuery("#displayExpiryJobCount").hide();
					}
				}
				
				
				var message = '(Displaying 1 to 25)';
				jQuery("#displayPageCountsDetails").html(message);
				/**********For changing counts on search pannel Top**************/
				var refinByDate='';
				if(refinByDate==null || refinByDate!='true' || refinByDate==''){
				jQuery("#clusterDataInitial").empty();
				jQuery("#clusterDataInitial").html(dataImageLoader);
				var htmlData = jQuery("#search-cluster-data").html();
				jQuery("#search-cluster-data").empty();
				jQuery("#clusterDataInitial").html(htmlData);
				/***************Start Ui Related hadling*************/
				//jQuery('.tj-tab-container  *:first-child').addClass('active');
				//var visclassch = jQuery('.refine-tab .tab li.active').attr(	"class");
				//visclassch = visclassch.replace(/active/, '');

						//.addClass('active').siblings().removeClass('active');
				if($.fn.slimscroll)	{
					jQuery('.cluster-scroll').slimscroll({
						height : '106px',
						railVisible : true
					});
				}
				
				
				showSelectedTabData('');

				jQuery('input:radio').parent('label').addClass('rdo');
				jQuery('input:radio:checked').parent('label').addClass(
						'radio-chkd');
				jQuery('input:radio').change(
						function() {
							var radioname = jQuery(this).attr('name');
							//alert(radioname);
							if (jQuery(this).is(':checked')
									|| jQuery('input:radio[name="' + radioname+ '"]').is(':checked')) {
								jQuery(this).parent('label').siblings()	.removeClass('radio-chkd');
								jQuery('input:radio[name="' + radioname + '"]').parent('label').removeClass('radio-chkd');
								jQuery(this).parent('label').addClass('radio-chkd');
							} else {
								jQuery(this).parent('label').removeClass(
										'radio-chkd');
							}
						});
					//chk bx script starts
					jQuery('input:checkbox').parent('label').addClass('chk');
					jQuery('input:checkbox:checked').parent('label').addClass('chk-chkd');
					jQuery('input:checkbox').change(function(){
						    if(jQuery(this).is(':checked')) {
					        jQuery(this).parent('label').addClass('chk-chkd');
					    } else {
					        jQuery(this).parent('label').removeClass('chk-chkd');
					    }
					});
					//chk bx script ends
				/***************End Ui Related hadling*************/				
				jQuery('.joblist > li:first-of-type').addClass('job-active')
						.find('.applybutton').removeClass('gray-btn');
				//jQuery('.comp-logo-bg').bgremove();
				
				}
				/*******************For hide Google ad sense Ifrmae if no result found**************/
				
			});
		function showMoreCompCluster(id){					
			if(id!=null  && id!='undefined' && id!=''){
				if(document.getElementById(id).style.display=='block'){					
					document.getElementById(id).style.display='none';
				}else{					
					document.getElementById(id).style.display='block';
				}
				
			}
		}		
		function showSelectedTabData(clusterName) {			
			var clusterArray = {
				'CLUSTER_FA' : 'tabjf',
				'CLUSTER_COMP' : 'tabtc',
				'CLUSTER_AOS' : 'tabjf',
				'CLUSTER_NRB' : 'tabloc',
				'CLUSTER_EXP' : 'tabexp',
				'CLUSTER_IND' : 'tabind',
				'CLUSTER_CTC' : 'tabsal'
			};
			var undoCluster={
					'cboPresFuncArea':'CLUSTER_FA',
					'compCluster':'CLUSTER_COMP',
					'funcAreaSpec':'CLUSTER_AOS',
					'locationCombo':'CLUSTER_NRB',
					'cboWorkExp1':'CLUSTER_EXP',
					'cboIndustry':'CLUSTER_IND',
					'txtLowSalary':'CLUSTER_CTC'				
			};		
			if(clusterName in undoCluster){
				console.info("Undo Value found with ClusterName="+undoCluster[clusterName]);
				clusterName=undoCluster[clusterName];			
			}
			if (chkNull(clusterName)) {
				console.info("inside showSelectedTabData clusterName="+clusterName);
					jQuery.each(clusterArray, function(key, value) {
						if (key == clusterName) {							
						var parentClusterTab=value.replace('tab','tab-');
						var indexOfParentTab=jQuery("#"+parentClusterTab).index();
						console.info("ui-tabs-activeId=="+parentClusterTab+ "parentTabId="+indexOfParentTab);
						jQuery( ".refined-bx" ).tabs("refresh");
						jQuery( ".refined-bx" ).tabs( "option", "active",indexOfParentTab);
							
						} 
					});
				
			}
		};
		
</script>

<script>


 
function logViewUSBT(action,adId,keySkill,location,exp,jobfun,rank,searchTextSrc)
{
	
	
	var skeyskills="";
	var slocation="";
	var sexperience="";  
	var sessionId="";
	var lsalary="";
	var hsalary="";
	var searchTextSrc="";
	
	
	/* console.log("+++++++++++++keyskills+++++++"+keySkill);
	console.log("+++++++++++++loc+++++++"+location);
	console.log("+++++++++++++exp+++++++"+exp);
	console.log("+++++++++jobfunc++++++"+jobfun);
	console.log("+++++adId++++++"+adId);
	console.log("+++++sessionIdI++++++"+sessionId); */
	var page = jQuery('em.active').text();
    
	console.log("page"+ page);
	var rp=rank+"-"+page;
	
	var field={s_skill:skeyskills, 
			    s_loc:slocation,
			    s_exp:sexperience,
			    s_lowsalary:lsalary,
			    s_highsalary:hsalary,
			    aId:adId,
			    rankPage:rp,
			    sid:sessionId,
			    j_fa:jobfun,
			    j_skill:keySkill,
			    j_location:location,
			    j_exp:exp};
	
	var usbt = {fields: field, actionType:action, skillSource: searchTextSrc};
	console.log("+++++++usbt++++++"+JSON.stringify(usbt));
	//var jsonString = JSON.stringify(usbt);
	ajaxController.logUSBTJobView(usbt,callbackusbt);
	
	
}

var callbackusbt = function (data){
	
}


	
</script>

<script type="text/template" id="searchBasedSkillgapTemplate">
 <div class="skill-gap-tags clearfix">
    {{#skillListKeywordBased}}
    	  <span class="tag2 tag-cls" id = "{{.}}">{{.}}<span class="tag-add material-icons" id="add{{.}}" onClick="addSkill('{{.}}',this);">add</span></span>

Max skill already added

 <script> 	
 	var profileSkills = '';
 	var resumeId = '';
	(function getSkillGapData(){
		var context="/candidate/";	 	
	 	var dataLoader="<img src='https://static.timesjobs.com/images_cand/tj_images/personlisation/loader.gif' alt='Loading' class='data-loading'>";
			jQuery.ajax({
						cache:false,
						url:context + "skillGapWidget.html?txtKeywords="+'',
						dataType:'json',
						beforeSend:function(){
							jQuery('#profileBasedSkillgap').html(dataLoader);
							console.log("beforeSend... skill gap");
						},
						success:function(jsonResp){
							var searchBasedSkillCount=jsonResp["skillListKeywordBasedCount"];
							var profileBasedSkillCount=jsonResp["skillValuesCount"];
							
							 var template = $('#skillGapWidgetTemplate').html();
	   	 					 var html = Mustache.to_html(template, jsonResp);
							//search base skill gap
							var searchBaseTemplate=$('#searchBasedSkillgapTemplate').html();
							var searchBaseHtml=Mustache.to_html(searchBaseTemplate, jsonResp);
	   	 					jQuery('#profileBasedSkillgap').html(html);
	   	 					jQuery('#searchBasedSkillgap').html(searchBaseHtml);
	   	 					 profileSkills = jsonResp.keySkills;
	   	 					 resumeId = jsonResp.adId;
	   	 					 if(profileBasedSkillCount<1 || profileBasedSkillCount<'1'){
	   	 						jQuery('#profileBasedSkillgap-spn').hide();
	   	 					 }
	   	 				 	if(searchBasedSkillCount<1 || searchBasedSkillCount<'1'){
	   	 						jQuery('#searchBasedSkillgap-spn').hide();
	   	 					 }
	   	 				 	if(searchBasedSkillCount<1 && profileBasedSkillCount<1){
	   	 				 		jQuery("#skill-gap-header-id").hide();
	   	 				 	}
	   	 				 	if(searchBasedSkillCount == undefined || profileBasedSkillCount == undefined){
	   	 				 		jQuery("#skill-gap-header-id").hide();
	   	 				 	}
	   	 				 	
	   	 					 
							},
						complete:function(){
							console.log("complete... skill gap");
							jQuery('#profileBasedSkillgap span.tag2:gt(4)').hide();	
							jQuery('#searchBasedSkillgap span.tag2:gt(4)').hide();
						}
					});
	})();
  function addSkill(skill,eleId){
  		ajaxController.isUserAuthenticated(function(response){
			if (response != null) {
				if (response == true) {
			  		addProfSkill(skill,eleId);
				}else{
						//var url="/candidate/ajaxLoginJobApply.html?fromPg=searchResultPage";
						//GB_showCenter('You are not logged in!', url, 350, 600);
						openModal.openLightBoxModal('loginLightboxModal.html?callFrom=searchResultPage', 'light-box-popup');
					}
				}
			});
  		
  }
  
  function addProfSkill(skill,eleId){  	
  		maxSkillCount = '50';
  		var skillCount = profileSkills.split(",").length;
  		if(skillCount < maxSkillCount){
  			var keySkills = profileSkills+","+skill;
			ajaxController.updateSkillsResumeWidget(keySkills,resumeId,function(data){
				jQuery(eleId).html('check');
				jQuery(eleId).parent().delay(1000).fadeOut(function(){ jQuery(this).remove(); });
				jQuery(eleId).parent().siblings('*:hidden:first').delay(1500).fadeIn();
			});
			profileSkills = keySkills;
		}else{
			document.getElementById('maxSkillErr').style.display='';
		}
  }
  
 
  </script>

			 <script type="text/javascript">
			      var cookieValue=getCookie('jobAlert');
			      window.setTimeout(onloadJobAlert, 10000 );			    
			     // deleteCookie('Job Alert');
			      function onloadJobAlert(){
			        	   //alert("gbcurrent"+GB_CURRENT);
			    	  if (cookieValue == null) {			   
			    		  //var _urlstr="jobAlert.html?txtKeywords=&cboWorkExp1=&txtLocation=&searchType=personalizedSearch";
			    		  //openModal.openLightBoxModal(_urlstr, 'light-box-popup');
			    		  GB_showCenter('Create a Job Alert','/candidate/jobAlert.html?txtKeywords=&cboWorkExp1=&txtLocation=',400, 340, callbackfun);
			    	  }
			       }
					
					function callbackfun(){
						var d = new Date();
						d.setTime(d.getTime()+(30*60*1000));
						setCookie('jobAlert',20,d);
						trackClickEvent('jobAlertSRP','jobAlertSRPClose');
						//alert("ankit");
					}
					</script>

<script type='text/javascript'>
	var tjtoken = '';
				if(tjtoken != null && tjtoken != ''){
					jQuery("#tgBannerCond").show();
				}else{
					jQuery.ajax({
				        url:"/candidate/userLoginDetails.json?source=TJWEB",
				        dataType:'json',
				        success:function(jsonResp){
					        tjtoken = jsonResp['tokenId'];
							jQuery("#tgBannerCond").show();
					    },
				        error: function(x, t, m) {
				        	if(t==="timeout") {
				                console.log("get token api ==== timeout");
				       		} else {
				        		console.log("error in get token === api called error");
				        	}
				    	},
				        complete:function(){
							console.log("get the token Success complete");
				        }
					});
			}
	function tgBannerConditionalOpen(){
		var redirectURL =  'https://www.techgig.com/codegladiators?utm_source=TJ_ITBatch&utm_medium=email&utm_campaign=TJ_Mailers&sourcetype=TJ_Mailer';
		if(tjtoken != null && tjtoken != undefined){
			redirectURL = 'https://www.techgig.com/codegladiators?tjtoken=' + tjtoken + '&utm_source=TJ_ITBatch&utm_medium=email&utm_campaign=TJ_Mailers&sourcetype=TJ_Mailer';
		}
		
		window.open(redirectURL, '_blank');
	}
</script>

<script>
function jobAlert(){
 GB_showCenter('Create a Job Alert','/candidate/jobAlert.html?txtKeywords=&cboWorkExp1=&txtLocation=',400,340,callbackfun);
 //var _urlstr="jobAlert.html?txtKeywords=&cboWorkExp1=&txtLocation=";
 //openModal.openLightBoxModal(_urlstr, 'light-box-popup');
}
var rootUrl='https://www.timesjobs.com/candidate/';
var app=angular.module("similarjobswidget",[]);
app.controller('bingoJobRecommendationController',function($scope,$http){
	///getrecojobs.json getsimilarprofileappliedjobs
$http.get(rootUrl+"getsimilarprofileappliedjobs.json?source=TJWEB&tokenId=").then(function(response){
	jQuery("#bingo-jobs-recommendation").show();
	if(response.data!=null && response.data.jobsResultBean!=null){
		$scope.bingoJobsList=response.data.jobsResultBean.jobList;
	}else{
		$scope.bingoJobsList=null;
	}		
	if(response.data!=null && response.data.jobsResultBean!=null && response.data.jobsResultBean.totalJobCount>0){
		$scope.totalAvailableJobs=response.data.jobsResultBean.totalJobCount;	
	}else{
		$scope.totalAvailableJobs=0;
		jQuery("#bingo-jobs-recommendation").hide();
	}
});
});
</script>

<script>
	var parameter="";
	var regFlow="";
	var loginFlow="";
	var applyFlow="";
		
	regFlow="false";
	loginFlow="false";
	applyFlow="false";
	
	if(regFlow=="true")
	{
		parameter="_registrationFlow";
		ajaxController.trackCounter(parameter, "reg_3p9901_exp");	
	}
	else if(loginFlow=="true"){
		var login = new RegExp("login.html", "i");
		if(!login.test(window.top.location) ){
			parameter="_loginFlow";
			ajaxController.trackCounter(parameter, "login_3p9901_exp");
		}
	}
	
	if(applyFlow=="true"){
		parameter="_applyFlow";
		ajaxController.trackCounter(parameter, "apply_3p9901_exp");
	}
</script>

				$(".registration-overlay, .registration-message").css("display", "none");
				updateStatus();
			}); */
	}
	/*
	$(window).on(
			'load',
			function() {
				$(".registration-overlay, .registration-message").css("display", "block");
			});
	*/
	$(".registration-close, .registration-btn-close").on("click", function() {
				$(".registration-overlay, .registration-message").css("display", "none");
				updateStatus();
			});
 
 
 	function updateStatus(){
		if(isFDivClosed === false){
			updateFraudBannerStatus();
		}
	}
	
	setTimeout(autoFDivClose, 30000);
	
	function autoFDivClose(){
		if(isFDivClosed === false){
			//updateFraudBannerStatus();
			isFDivClosed = true;
			$(".registration-overlay, .registration-message").css("display", "none");
		}
	}
	
	function updateFraudBannerStatus(){
		var context="/candidate/";
		jQuery.ajax({
 					url:context + 'updateFraudBannerStatus.json?&source=TJWEB',
 					beforeSend:function(){
						console.log("beforeSend... updateFraudBannerStatus");
						},
					success:function(jsonResp){
   	 					 console.log('updateFraudBannerStatus loaded successfully : ',jsonResp)
						},
					complete:function(){
						console.log("complete... updateFraudBannerStatus");
						isFDivClosed = true;
						$(".registration-overlay, .registration-message").css("display", "none");
					}
 				});
	}
	
	function getFraudBannerShowStatus(){
		var context="/candidate/";
		jQuery.ajax({
 					url:context + 'getFraudBannerShowStatus.json?&source=TJWEB',
 					beforeSend:function(){
						console.log("beforeSend... updateFraudBannerStatus");
						},
					success:function(jsonResp){
   	 					 console.log('updateFraudBannerStatus loaded successfully : ',jsonResp)
   	 					 console.log('jsonResp : ',jsonResp)
   	 					 if(jsonResp != null && jsonResp['showfraudbanner'] != null && jsonResp['showfraudbanner'] === true){
   	 					 	isFDivClosed = false;
   	 					 	registerFraudBannerEvents();
   	 					 }
						},
					complete:function(){
						
					}
 				});
	}
	
	
		
</script>

<script type="text/javascript">
		var userFirstName_ =  '';
		function handleCredentialResponse(response) {
		  // Here we can do whatever process with the response we want
		  // Note that response.credential is a JWT ID token
		  console.log("Encoded JWT ID token: " + response.credential);
		  console.log('All : ',response)
		  googleOneTapLogin(response.credential);
		}
		window.onload = function () {
		  google.accounts.id.initialize({
		    client_id: "819793255355-3574gl7e6o6pkq7cc46dedolg7hae69k.apps.googleusercontent.com", // Replace with your Google Client ID
		    callback: handleCredentialResponse, // We choose to handle the callback in client side, so we include a reference to a function that will handle the response
		    //login_uri: "http://localhost:8080/gots/callback"
		    //ux_mode: "redirect",
		    //auto_select="false"
		    cancel_on_tap_outside: false
		  });
		  
		  // You can skip the next instruction if you don't want to show the "Sign-in" button
		  /* google.accounts.id.renderButton(
	      	document.getElementById("g_id_signin"),
	      	{ theme: "outline", size: "large" }  // customization attributes
	        ); */
	      
		  google.accounts.id.prompt((notification) =>{
		  	if(notification.isDisplayMoment()){
		  		let moment_ = notification.getMomentType();
		  		console.log(" .......... Google One Tap Moment : "+moment_);
		  	}
		  	if(notification.isDisplayed()){
		  		console.log(" .......... Google One Tap Displayed");
		  		$('#modalwrap').show();
		  	}
		  	if(notification.isNotDisplayed()){
		  		let notDisplayReason = notification.getNotDisplayedReason();
		  		console.log(" .......... Google One Tap Not Displayed Reason : "+notDisplayReason)
		  	}
		  	if(notification.isSkippedMoment()){
		  		let skip_reason = notification.getSkippedReason();
		  		console.log(" .......... Google One Tap Dismissed : "+skip_reason)
		  		$('#modalwrap').hide();
		  	}
		  	if(notification.isDismissedMoment()){
		  		let dismissReason = notification.getDismissedReason();
		  		console.log(" .......... Google One Tap Dismissed : "+dismissReason)
		  		$('#modalwrap').hide();
		  	}
		  	
		  }); // Display the One Tap dialog
		  
		}
		function googleOneTapLogin(jwt){
			
			var context="/candidate/";
			jQuery.ajax({
 					url:context + "googleonetaplogin.json?source=gTap&jwt="+jwt+"&curl="+encodeURIComponent(window.location.href),
 					beforeSend:function(){
						console.log("beforeSend... googleonetaplogin");
						},
					success:function(jsonResp){
   	 					 console.log('success ... googleonetaplogin : ',jsonResp)
   	 					 if(jsonResp != null && jsonResp["rurl"] != null){
					   	 	window.location.href = jsonResp["rurl"];
   	 					 }
						},
					complete:function(){
						console.log("complete... loadBannerCampaigns");
					}
 				});
		}
		
</script>

<script type='text/javascript'>
/*!
* jQuery Cookie Plugin v1.3.1
* https://github.com/carhartl/jquery-cookie
*
* Copyright 2013 Klaus Hartl
* Released under the MIT license
*/
(function (factory) {
if (typeof define === 'function' && define.amd && define.amd.jQuery) {
// AMD. Register as anonymous module.
define(['jquery'], factory);
} else {
// Browser globals.
factory(jQuery);
}
}(function ($) {

var pluses = /\+/g;

function raw(s) {
return s;
}

function decoded(s) {
return decodeURIComponent(s.replace(pluses, ' '));
}

function converted(s) {
if (s.indexOf('"') === 0) {
// This is a quoted cookie as according to RFC2068, unescape
s = s.slice(1, -1).replace(/\\"/g, '"').replace(/\\\\/g, '\\');
}
try {
return config.json ? JSON.parse(s) : s;
} catch(er) {}
}

var config = $.cookie = function (key, value, options) {

// write
if (value !== undefined) {
options = $.extend({}, config.defaults, options);

if (typeof options.expires === 'number') {
var days = options.expires, t = options.expires = new Date();
t.setDate(t.getDate() + days);
}

value = config.json ? JSON.stringify(value) : String(value);

return (document.cookie = [
encodeURIComponent(key), '=', config.raw ? value : encodeURIComponent(value),
options.expires ? '; expires=' + options.expires.toUTCString() : '', // use expires attribute, max-age is not supported by IE
options.path ? '; path=' + options.path : '',
options.domain ? '; domain=' + options.domain : '',
options.secure ? '; secure' : ''
].join(''));
}

// read
var decode = config.raw ? raw : decoded;
var cookies = document.cookie.split('; ');
var result = key ? undefined : {};
for (var i = 0, l = cookies.length; i < l; i++) {
var parts = cookies[i].split('=');
var name = decode(parts.shift());
var cookie = decode(parts.join('='));

if (key && key === name) {
result = converted(cookie);
break;
}

if (!key) {
result[name] = converted(cookie);
}
}

return result;
};

config.defaults = {};

$.removeCookie = function (key, options) {
if ($.cookie(key) !== undefined) {
$.cookie(key, '', $.extend(options, { expires: -1 }));
return true;
}
return false;
};

}));
</script>

	//setCookie('current_browser_url', window.location.href);
</script>
	<script type="text/javascript">
	function getPredefinedActionName(url){
		var returnActionName = "";
		var from = url.lastIndexOf("/");
		var to = url.indexOf("?",from);
		if(-1!=to){
			returnActionName = url.substring(from,to);
		}else{
			returnActionName = url.substring(from);
		}
		return returnActionName;
	}
	</script>
